// Modal form component that users will set their filters. import { useEffect, useState } from 'react'; import ReactModal from 'react-modal'; export default function FilterForm({childSetMandatory, childSetOptional, childSetSort}) { function formReset() { document.getElementById("filterForm").reset(); } // modal visibility state and toggle const [isModalOpen, setisModalOpen] = useState(false); function openModal() { setisModalOpen(true); document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden'; } // useEffect() function updateAll() { let min_power_value = document.getElementById('min_power').value; setisModalOpen(false) document.body.style.overflow = 'unset'; childSetMandatory({ min_power: {min_power_value}, max_power: 7000, min_power_bonus: 0.1, max_power_bonus: 1, min_attr_bonus: 0, max_attr_bonus: 1, min_luck: 0, max_luck: 500, min_title_req: 0, max_title_req: 15, min_cheese_effect: 0, max_cheese_effect: 12, }) } return ( <>
